<br>
As she walked, somehting in the water caught her eye. A shimmering , oil like substance. She knelt down and touched it, bringing it up with her fingers, she smelt it, then wrinkled her nose.  Just as she thought. Hydra blood. Something, it seemed, had hurt the beast enough to make it bleed.<br>
<br>
She got up, and began walking. She was walking with the current, she knew it was the right way. <p>~ The Silver Goddess~&lt;br&gt;<br>
